pedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"ease\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"her disappointment\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1061}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"unnecessary noises\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked whether the strange atmosphere inside the Bercy Arena was the reason for her outburst, Biles told Eurosport: 'Yes, and we have asked for music several times but they do not want to play some music for some reason.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the strange atmosphere\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"the Bercy Arena\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"her outburst\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"Eurosport\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1264}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"some music\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"some reason\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But I think the shushing was the loudest part.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shushing\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"the loudest part\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their shushing and their trying to cheer\\u2026 it was so weird and odd but it is what it is at the end of the day.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1517}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Beam is always a tough apparatus to do a final on and unfortunately, for a lot of us, it did not happen today.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Beam\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough apparatus\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But that's okay because we are still proud of whoever made the podium.'\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whoever\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite missing out on gold on the beam and on the floor, Biles said she was 'definitely proud' to take four medals back to the United States.\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1846, \"end\": 1859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9556876697610628, \"rank\": 0.02514982644609515, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"the beam\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"four medals\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am definitely proud of the work that I have put in mentally and physically,' she added.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Having the right group of people around me\\u2026 it just goes to show that I can do it and I did it here a couple of nights in a row.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right group\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"nights\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am really proud of the work and outcomes.\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"outcomes\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not be disappointed with any of my performances that I have done here at the Games.'\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my performances\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles' success in Paris comes three years after her Tokyo 'twisties' which forced her to pull out of several events.\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.414609526243288e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2274, \"end\": 2279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999660119929866, \"rank\": 3.122008082797393e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles' success\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2236}, {\"ngram\": \"several events\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if she felt like she had redeemed herself, Biles replied: 'Most definitely.\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I could not be more proud of how I have done.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am 27 years old and walking away from this Games with four medals to add to my collection.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this Games\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"four medals\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"my collection\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not mad about it.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'And always sharing the podium with Jordan [Chiles] is so much fun.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2623, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.5018404198269524, \"rank\": 0.5233078129023155, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"so much fun\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have trained together for so many years so to see her put in that hard work and for it to pay off is just amazing.\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many years\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"that hard work\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think I was more excited for her than I was for myself!'\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pressed on how she will celebrate her experience at the Games, Biles responded: 'Maybe a tattoo.\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her experience\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2883}, {\"ngram\": 